OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale released in
OL,4,CNorth Sea after weeks stranded
OL,6,FA humpback whale that had been
OL,7,Fstranded in shallow waters near
OL,8,FGermany since March has finally been
OL,9,Freleased into the North Sea, rescuers
OL,10,Fsay.
OL,12,FNicknamed "Timmy" by German media, the
OL,13,Fwhale was spotted swimming near the
OL,14,Fcoast of the Baltic Sea on March 3,
OL,15,Ffar from his natural habitat in the
OL,16,FAtlantic Ocean.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
