PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777810266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale released in
OL,4,CNorth Sea after weeks stranded
OL,6,FThe young male's health had
OL,7,Fdeteriorated as he became repeatedly
OL,8,Fstranded in shallow waters near the
OL,9,Fcoastal city of Wismar, with attempts
OL,10,Fto coax him toward deeper seas proving
OL,11,Funsuccessful.
OL,13,FHis ordeal gained plenty of public
OL,14,Fattention in Germany, with local media
OL,15,Fproducing dayslong livestreams on the
OL,16,Frescue effort and online newspapers
OL,17,Fblasting push alerts on the smallest
OL,18,Fupdates on Timmy's health.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777810266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale released in
OL,4,CNorth Sea after weeks stranded
OL,6,FThe environment minister for Germany's
OL,7,FMecklenburg-Western Pomerania state
OL,8,Fgave the green light for the attempt
OL,9,Fto save the whale, proposed by a
OL,10,Fprivate initiative.
OL,12,FThis was despite some warnings from
OL,13,Fthe scientific community that the move
OL,14,Fwould cause severe stress to an
OL,15,Falready sick animal.
OL,17,FRescuers spent hours getting Timmy
OL,18,Fonto a flooded barge, guiding him
OL,19,Fthrough a specially dredged channel
OL,20,Fand using straps to pull him onto the
OL,21,Fvessel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777810266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale released in
OL,4,CNorth Sea after weeks stranded
OL,6,FJens Schwarck, a member of the private
OL,7,Finitiative who was on site, said the
OL,8,Fwhale was released around 9am local
OL,9,Ftime on Saturday, according to the
OL,10,FGerman news agency dpa.
OL,12,FThe agency reported that the whale was
OL,13,Freleased about 45 miles from the coast
OL,14,Fof Skagen, Denmark. His ordeal is not
OL,15,Fover yet, as it is hoped he will find
OL,16,Fthe strength to swim further to the
OL,17,FAtlantic Ocean.
OL,19,FA debate emerged about whether to let
OL,20,Fthe whale die in peace or try to
OL,21,Fassist his return home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
