FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777810266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale released in
OL,4,CNorth Sea after weeks stranded
OL,6,FActivists staged protests on the beach
OL,7,Fin Wismar calling for his liberation,
OL,8,Fwhile others have supported new ideas
OL,9,Fabout how the whale could be
OL,10,Ftransported.
OL,12,FSome scientists believe the whale had
OL,13,Fsearched for shallow waters because he
OL,14,Fwas weak and needed rest. The
OL,15,Fveterinarians of the private
OL,16,Finitiative, however, considered the
OL,17,Fanimal fit for transport.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
