PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777810266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale released in
OL,4,CNorth Sea after weeks stranded
OL,6,FBefore the release, a GPS transmitter
OL,7,Fwas reportedly attached to track the
OL,8,Fwhale's future location, according to
OL,9,Fdpa.
OL,11,FIt is not clear why the whale swam so
OL,12,Ffar from his natural habitat.
OL,14,FSome experts say the animal may have
OL,15,Flost his way while swimming after a
OL,16,Fshoal of herring or during migration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
