PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777810266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale released in
OL,4,CNorth Sea after weeks stranded
OL,6,FSince then, the mammal became
OL,7,Frepeatedly stranded in shallow waters.
OL,8,FHe was in clear distress, breathing
OL,9,Firregularly and often barely moving
OL,10,Ffor days.
OL,12,FTimmy also suffered from a bad skin
OL,13,Fcondition, related to the Baltic Sea's
OL,14,Flow salt content, and rescuers applied
OL,15,Fkilos of zinc ointment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
